`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:'IIIT Kottayam attracts summer applicants because its labs blend core engineering with translational work tied to industry and national missions. This playbook focuses on how to win a seat in 2026: where to look, when to outreach, and how to avoid the common mistakes that sink otherwise strong profiles. Any date or stipend notes marked as "Expected / Indicative" mirror recent cycles and help you move early; update your plan when official circulars post.'}),`
