`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"IIT Patna operates in Patna, Bihar, giving interns access to regional industries and research ecosystems. The campus hosts active centers spanning AI/ML and data science, Robotics and mechatronics, VLSI and embedded systems and collaborates with government and industry sponsors. If you are comparing across the IIT system, anchor your choices with the IIT internships hub to see where this institute leads on depth, facilities, and sponsored work."}),`
